{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"alias":"calicoed-shaded-seahog","creation_channel":"cli","description":"## Problem\nA source citation [rebar:<id>] from a child requires a DIRECT verified edge from the citing ticket to the cited target; a transitive/inherited edge does not satisfy it. Combined with link's hierarchy promotion (blocking deps on a story are promoted to the parent epic by design), a child's citation to a prerequisite is left ungrounded with no obvious cause.\n\n## Design (per maintainer)\nCitation validation must honor INHERITED links. Epic A has Child B; Child B cites Epic C. Epics depend on Epics and Stories depend on Stories. So as long as Epic A (B's parent) depends_on Epic C, the citation in Child B to Epic C is valid via inheritance from the parent's edge.\n\n## Fix\nWhen validating a [rebar:<id>] citation from a ticket T to target X, treat the citation as grounded if EITHER (a) T has a direct verified edge to X (current behavior), OR (b) an ancestor of T (walk parent_id chain) has a direct verified depends_on/blocking edge to X (or to an ancestor of X at the matching hierarchy level). Preserve current direct-edge behavior; only ADD the inherited path.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- A citation from Child B to Epic C is VALID when B's parent Epic A depends_on Epic C, with no direct B->C edge.\n- A citation with neither a direct nor an inherited edge remains INVALID (no over-grounding).\n- Existing direct-edge citations remain valid (no regression).\n- Tests cover: inherited-valid, direct-valid, neither-invalid.\n\n## Verification\npytest citation-validation tests for the three cases above.","id":"a1a2-f491-84e3-4f21","parent_id":"56c0-1d2f-f39c-4ac1","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"bug","title":"[rebar:<id>] citation validation should honor inherited hierarchy links"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1784776562456426001,"uuid":"cfb71892-5342-48db-b601-501614a5e964"}